high_descs: Walk straight to the sofa ahead.
Pick up the knife from the sofa.
Go to the table with the microwave to your left.
Place the knife on the plate next to the microwave.
Pick up the plate with the knife in it.
Turn around and go straight into the doorway ahead to the bathroom.
Place the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a knife on it in a bathroom sink.

high_descs: Head straight to reach the sofa.
Pick up the knife from the sofa.
Turn around and head right to reach the plate on the dining table.
Put the knife on the plate on the table.
Pick up the plate from the dining table.
Turn around to head to the sink on the left.
Put the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with knife in the sink.

high_descs: Walk straight to the sofa in front of you.
Pick up the knife on the sofa.
Turn around, go straight towards the wall in front of you, hang a right and head straight to the plate on the table.
Put the knife in the plate on the table.
Pick up the plate with the knife on the table.
Turn right, go straight to the sofa, hang a right and go straight to the wall, then turn left and enter the washroom to your right and go to the sink.
Put the plate with the knife in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a knife inside a sink.
